OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fperhaps heavy with thunder, lingering
OL,7,Finto the evening before gradually
OL,8,Ffading. Becoming dry overnight, with
OL,9,Fprolonged clear spells. Turning
OL,10,Fchilly, with some frost mainly in
OL,11,Fprone rural spots. Some isolated mist
OL,12,Fand fog patches. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA bright, chilly start, but
OL,15,Fcloud thickening from the west.
OL,16,FOutbreaks of light rain, mainly for
OL,17,Fwestern areas, during the afternoon.
OL,18,FSome brightness lingering in the east.
OL,19,FTurning breezy. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
